<section id="pfeile">
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148798" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="3">Detective arrows in the document are updated under the following circumstances:</paragraph>
<list type="unordered">
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3153192" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="4">Starting <emph>Tools - Detective - Update Refresh Traces</emph>
</paragraph>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<paragraph role="listitem" id="par_id3151041" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="5">If <emph>Tools - Detective - Update Automatically</emph> is turned on, every time formulas are changed in the document.</paragraph>
</listitem>
</list>
</section>
